RetryBuildStep
/ Retries step building after validation failure
/ LLM gets the error message and previous result to fix

- read file "llm/FixStep.llm", load vars, write to %fixStepPrompt%
- [llm] system: %fixStepPrompt%
        user: Step: %step.Text%
              Intent: %step.Description%
              Previous result: %stepResult%
              Error: %!error%
        scheme: {method: string, data: {type: string, data: object}, return?: string, onError?: object, cache?: object, cancelAfterSeconds?: int, errors: [string], warnings: [string]}
        write to %stepResult%
- [plang] Validate %step.ModuleType%, %stepResult.method%, %stepResult.data%
    on error call HandleBuildStepFailure
